	<summary><b>$_COOKIE</b> is an array variable that contains the data for all cookies set in the visiting browser.</summary>

	<examples>
<example>put $_COOKIE into tCookiesArray</example>
<example><p>put $_COOKIE[&quot;user&quot;] into tUser</p><p></p></example>
<example><p>if $_COOKIE[&quot;user&quot;] is not empty then</p><p>  -- ... pre-populate user login Id ...</p><p>end if</p></example>
